  "A movie theater sells adult tickets for $12 and child tickets for $8. If 200 tickets were sold for a total of $2,000, how many adult tickets were sold?": "",
  "150": "",
  "80": "",
  "100": "",
  "120": "",
  "Let a + c = 200 and 12a + 8c = 2000. Substitute c = 200 - a: 12a + 8(200-a) = 2000, 4a = 400, a = 100 adult tickets.": "",
  "A farmer has chickens and cows. There are 30 animals and 86 legs total. How many cows does the farmer have?": "",
  "20": "",
  "15": "",
  "13": "",
  "17": "",
  "c + w = 30 and 2c + 4w = 86. From c = 30 - w: 2(30-w) + 4w = 86, 60 + 2w = 86, w = 13 cows.": "",
  "A school fundraiser sells candy bars at $2 and popcorn at $3. The group sold 150 items for $380. How many candy bars were sold?": "",
  "70": "",
  "90": "",
  "60": "",
  "c + p = 150 and 2c + 3p = 380. Substitute p = 150 - c: 2c + 3(150-c) = 380, -c = -70, c = 70.": "",
